{"tid":1639132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如要利用NBA事件請幫香港和大陸黑人平權爭取美國人支持","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T13:08:47.000Z","uid":322195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba8b88321b8778908c3f9a33c763dadde7362e0","tid":1639132,"uid":322195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"香港同大陸都有大量黑人（For Example 廣州）長期比警察同公安武警欺凌歧視而被禁聲.大家唔好忘記美國仲有大量美國黑人我地未Connect. 無需要用低莊手段，我地要用正義幫呢班人爭取。例如James Harden 向CCP道歉已經得罪所有大陸嘅黑人（有幾十萬），黑人係超級團結的，我地絕對需要佢地嘅票。可以做文宣tweet Obama 同佢嘅盟友 #StandWithHongKong"},{"pid":"1bbe99e68a75a80cf795428641182da40a4b3bfa","tid":1639132,"uid":322195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"唔係要比黑人咩福利，我識嘅大部份黑人只想被當成係一個人，警察通常都唔當佢地係人而且極冇禮貌"},{"pid":"5fd170d0bc0f04eb5f27bc84a2467ecdf1556acd","tid":1639132,"uid":127176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"idea係支持<br />\n不過係香港黑人真係冇咩人會留意到（好多香港人連南亞人都唔會係生活上接觸到，更何況人口更少、文化更陌生嘅非洲黑人）<br />\n亦冇咩資料可以做文宣"},{"pid":"a0ce86778a96ba0118901ceac2b8524fd7db154d","tid":1639132,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"[行動POST] 想要靚畫面？銀髮族48小時靜坐咪就係機會囉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648992</a><br />\n<br />\n警總靜坐現場，有老人有中年人有外國人有後生仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多中年帶哂席同櫈黎，準備過夜。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">想有新行動？想要靚畫面？咁你就快啲過黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日攰唔出都唔緊要，準備聽日接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我煲大佢，唔好當銀髮手足係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAwXWg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAwXWg8.jpg&h=aab0f8a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33b545aef20d25965adfe70493e1ff0321fe4da9","tid":1639132,"uid":205520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fd170d0bc0f04eb5f27bc84a2467ecdf1556acd","tid":1639132,"uid":127176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"idea係支持<br />\n不過係香港黑人真係冇咩人會留意到（好多香港人連南亞人都唔會係生活上接觸到，更何況人口更少、文化更陌生嘅非洲黑人）<br />\n亦冇咩資料可以做文宣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}